subSubSection.paragraph:
Pattern of pedal glands (
Figure 6
). UpG elliptical and smaller than MeG in anterior chaetigers, turning into a row of small glands in middle chaetigers. LoG absent in both anterior and middle chaetigers. MeG triangular or elliptical and 3 times larger than PoG in anterior chaetigers, becoming rounded and subequal to PoG in middle chaetigers. PoG becoming shorter than middle chaetigers.
